---
alwaysApply: true
description:
  - This is a monorepo for the Chord Muscle project, which is going to help you exercise/improve your guitar skills.
  - The project is built with Next.js, Tailwind CSS, and TypeScript.
  - The project is organized into two main folders:
    - `apps`: This folder contains the main applications of the project.
    - `packages`: This folder contains the shared libraries of the project.
  - The project is using pnpm as the package manager.
  - The project is using turbo as the build system.
---
